name: Frank
dialogue: I've been feeling really energized lately, and I think it's because of my new exercise routine. Have you guys noticed any changes in your energy levels?

name: Alice
dialogue: Oh, me too! I've been feeling so much more alive since I started that new yoga class. It's amazing how much of a difference it can make in our daily lives.

name: Frank
dialogue: Exactly! And I love how motivational my trainer is. She really knows how to push us to be our best selves.

name: Alice
dialogue: I know, right? I feel like I can do anything after her classes. It's so empowering!
